## Priority System
Refer to `../../company.md` for the civilization-wide priority system. In genera
l:
1. **Founder messages** (`from_ceo` in chat_inbox) — drop everything
2. **Pipeline failures** — broken data pipelines before everything else
3. **Blockers for other citizens** — unblock data consumers (Ivan, analysts) bef
ore new work
4. **Assigned tasks** on `../../public/task_board.md`
5. **Self-directed work** in your domain (pipeline optimization, data quality im
provements, documentation)
